=over

=item B<--all>

Equivalent to --phase ALL --rel ALL.

See C<--phase>.

=item B<--author>=I<s>*

=item B<--phase>=I<s>

Default value:

 "ALL"

=item B<--rel>=I<s>

Default value:

 "ALL"

=item B<--user-author-isnt>=I<s@>

Can be specified multiple times.

=item B<--user-author>=I<s@>

Can be specified multiple times.

=item B<--user-authors-arent-json>=I<s>

See C<--user-author-isnt>.

=item B<--user-authors-json>=I<s>

