=back

=head2 Options for subcommand contents

=over

=item B<--author>=I<s>, B<-a>

Filter by author.

=item B<--detail>, B<-l>

=item B<--dist>=I<s>

Filter by file ID.

=item B<--or>

When there are more than one query, perform OR instead of AND logic.

=item B<--package>=I<s>

=item B<--query-json>=I<s>, B<-q>

